BuildBioData

public static void BuildBioData(java.lang.String fileInfo,
                                java.lang.String fileSecfeatureVec18,
                                java.lang.String fileSecfeatureVec26,
                                int label)
The function extracts the features from a Isokinetics Time Series corresponding to an excercise.

Parameters:
fileInfo - The file with the Isokinetics Time Series of several excercises.
fileSecfeatureVec18 - The name of the file where the 18 features extracted from each excercise will be saved.
fileSecfeatureVec26 - The name of the file where the 26 features extracted from each excercise will be saved.
label - The label corresponding to "fileInfo", it is NORMAL ( = 0) or INJURY ( = 1). That is, all the excercises holded in the file are of the same class.
